title: #137 - Spiderman Fired From MCU & Arby's Taste Test Nightmare
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast Ethan and Hila talk about their new mobility scooter, taste test a bunch of garbage food from Arby's, the Amazon forest being on fire, Spider-man getting fired from the MCU, celeberties falling for your grandma's chain emails, and a whole lot more!
